---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="Validator as a service" id="intro">
  <Icon slot="eyebrow" name="logomark" class="h-32" />
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    We provide you with effortless and instant validator deployment for the
    blockchain of your choice with a simple user interface including service
    control and monitoring. Updates are configured to be automatic, done in a
    seamless fashion without downtime as long as the blockchain offers session
    key swapping. True
    <span class="text-primary">decentralization</span> requires <span
      class="text-primary">powerful tools</span
    > that anyone is able to use.
  </Fragment>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <a
      href="https://rotko.net/docs"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="telescope" class="h-8" />
      <span>Explore our Docs</span>
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://app.rotko.net/"
      class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border-2 border-current px-6 py-4"
    >
      <Icon pack="mdi" name="rocket" class="h-8" />
      <span>Try our App</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
